<item>
            <title>[SPARK-4532] make-distribution in Spark 1.2 does not correctly detect whether Hive is enabled</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-4532</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I noticed that Hive support isn&apos;t working in the recent release artifacts. Because the hive profile is no longer defined in the root pom, the following doesn&apos;t work:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;SPARK_HIVE=$(mvn help:evaluate -Dexpression=project.activeProfiles $@ 2&amp;gt;/dev/&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;\
    | grep -v &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;INFO&quot;&lt;/span&gt;\
    | fgrep --count &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&amp;lt;id&amp;gt;hive&amp;lt;/id&amp;gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;;\
    # Reset exit status to 0, otherwise the script stops here &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; the last grep finds nothing\
    # because we use &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;set -o pipefail&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
    echo -n)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We need to simply change it to this&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;SPARK_HIVE=$(mvn help:evaluate -Dexpression=project.activeProfiles -pl sql/hive $@ 2&amp;gt;/dev/&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;\
    | grep -v &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;INFO&quot;&lt;/span&gt;\
    | fgrep --count &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&amp;lt;id&amp;gt;hive&amp;lt;/id&amp;gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;;\
    # Reset exit status to 0, otherwise the script stops here &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; the last grep finds nothing\
    # because we use &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;set -o pipefail&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
    echo -n)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
